<taxonomicName id="AF736E65B033A4B9B0F6BBC511A5BEA5" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Schizoceratomyia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Schizoceratomyia" order="Diptera" pageId="62" pageNumber="63" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Schizoceratomyia</taxonomicName>
Carrera, Lopes &amp; Lane, 1947a: 245. Type species: 
<taxonomicName id="B3E8A15CD481CEF523FD8E3C80CC0A47" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Schizoceratomyia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Schizoceratomyia barretoi" order="Diptera" pageId="62" pageNumber="63" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="barretoi">Schizoceratomyia barretoi</taxonomicName>
Carrera, Lopes &amp; Lane 1947a: 245, by original designation.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="DEE9FE316BC99F63301CB0F9DEA74A2C" pageId="62" pageNumber="63">
<taxonomicName id="27CFFAA67F8A9F936E3C84132054BCF3" authority="Curran, 1947" authorityName="Curran" authorityYear="1947" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Johnsoniodon" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Johnsoniodon" order="Diptera" pageId="62" pageNumber="63" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Johnsoniodon</taxonomicName>
Curran, 1947: 1. Type species: 
<taxonomicName id="4307137959E01A9290251E87C58FBE57" authority="Curran, 1947" authorityName="Curran" authorityYear="1947" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Johnsoniodon" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Johnsoniodon malleri" order="Diptera" pageId="62" pageNumber="63" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="malleri">Johnsoniodon malleri</taxonomicName>
Curran, 1947: 1, by original designation. See 
<bibRefCitation id="D6BCF8903A5EF0CB43E268AE2DE3E400" author="Papavero, N" journalOrPublisher="Papeis Avulsos do Departamento de Zoologia" pageId="85" pageNumber="86" pagination="317 - 326" title="Quatro novas especies de Microdontinae do Brasil (Diptera, Syrphidae)." volume="15" year="1962">Papavero (1962)</bibRefCitation>
for synonymy.
</paragraph>
